OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FOfsted to reinspect some   
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Finadequate schools sooner  
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Schools in England which are given an  
OL,6, Ofsted rating of inadequate over child 
OL,7, welfare will be reinspected sooner to  
OL,8, give them a chance to improve.         
OL,10,FIt is one of several reforms being made
OL,11,Fin response to the death of head       
OL,12,Fteacher Ruth Perry, who took her own   
OL,13,Flife following an Ofsted inspection.   
OL,15,FMrs Perry's family and a head teachers'
OL,16,Funion say the measures are a start, but
OL,17,Ffar bigger changes are needed.         
OL,19,FOfsted defended its one-word ratings   
OL,20,Fsystem, which is not being scrapped.   
